    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Anthropic just published a thirty-five-page playbook, and the first warning is that Claude Code will help you fail FASTER.",
      "checksum": "sha256:924bfda4a520b39631f4ea5d31ca3edfce96b107dc4eb65a35a1620e381220bd",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 6.780226757369615,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Page ten: forty-two percent of startups failed building something nobody wanted. And the playbook says that number is only going to climb.",
      "checksum": "sha256:628ee0cd9efac99c7b2ecfc4a09139027a8cdfeed34fcf9c8e7e0f384bb47fb3",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 8.080544217687075,
      "word_count": 22,
      "words_offset": 19
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Which is why Mike Krieger, Instagram's co-founder, said publicly he could have built Instagram with just himself and his co-founder using Claude today.",
      "checksum": "sha256:126e30d54cd96d81806779934f18e7cddc374bfdb3b127a95c69a7619c5277c7",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 8.684263038548753,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 41
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Krieger said it. Anthropic just made it operational.",
      "checksum": "sha256:afe66b62766485ca13975614e3cba94408cd521f04fe68478e0bcbf598642707",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 64
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "So Anthropic remapped startup building into four stages.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f43a19da7809bee69760684db4119ff50d24acff64d12058a00d134d2bdce1f9",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 72
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Idea. M V P. Launch. Scale. Each one has a goal, an exit test, and a failure mode.",
      "checksum": "sha256:593cfef61050cbe71116dc28badd88eff73b571997b32a000cf9d790adb2271a",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 6.130068027210885,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 80
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Idea is finding a problem worth paying for.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f98de9ba84a3679f0de5098235ab4cab0fe05e67861f8b0ed1b32d8188fa7686",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 98
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "M V P is proving people actually will. Launch is going from one founder to a small team.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a6fc498e7af27b92203949a089b254eb109496c34b546b948e94d1e2ca106221",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 5.2477097505668935,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 106
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "And Scale is when every decision still going through you stops being an asset, and starts being the bottleneck.",
      "checksum": "sha256:24559e8b7d63b50ad934481423ad2901a24ce3aa1822c4870df8acc94014c2e4",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 6.408707482993197,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 124
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Each stage has a named killer. Idea stage.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5aa547a63bcd96bc026c0d8b95e2fd1bf7d009e762c9e9dd15c32cf695f8b275",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 143
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Mistaking building for validating. You ship a prototype in four hours and call it proof.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8ccdbf89f240db8c759cc7ad00166667dcda763a7666420d93dd386e09b352c4",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 4.876190476190477,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 151
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "M V P stage. Agentic technical debt. Skip the specs and every Claude session drifts the codebase further from your plan.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7bc1ae623a89e597bd3f2b062174bb7293b566ccd369afac3d475a00b2c63fb9",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 7.75546485260771,
      "word_count": 21,
      "words_offset": 166
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Launch stage. The founder becomes the bottleneck.",
      "checksum": "sha256:be0c3e915a3e175180b57d2faa8e2760ca0a53d2f346333e45422f12fecc2455",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 187
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Decisions that should take an hour now take a week.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c4713495ad6c962ee3134a22eb68b1d14fc332c76eba2ce71eb5289c062de26c",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 194
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Scale stage. Delegating the operational layer.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c3a4e6ac51dfdf677c4f67880b2c3514965b34a66c16f9019445e9f0a7317e23",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 204
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "You built the systems, and now you have to actually trust them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:de26bfb1d75996a8417851643ee61aa25a3efa48df5c26f71536d7f381467fc8",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 210
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Four stages. Four named ways to die. So which Claude do you reach for first?",
      "checksum": "sha256:4d791f70c4ba97fe9b10d931cd45f47b81098b42b7328d5ffcef49c5488be363",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 4.829750566893424,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 222
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "Plus, page eleven publishes a decision table.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f894a424709215d0e1b2270ac14bd5390cb24d0e4a07efb14eb941d6c485335c",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 237
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Three surfaces, same brain, different jobs.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fd38a99d51725587416e6575f67d767f7a412cfd60f6722ec52ecfba03bcc9c9",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 244
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "Chat for quick exchanges. Claude Cowork for knowledge work.",
      "checksum": "sha256:da3bed924c34a4202816bee7b2ca02ab1e81c0e52cb66e957167850951435429",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 2.9257142857142857,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 250
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "Claude Code for the codebase. Pick wrong, you waste hours.",
      "checksum": "sha256:05b46b333747bf4e3dc203a5c686ca0ba642337d1ca81f340435c8599a4380e7",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 259
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "Here's what running it actually looks like.",
      "checksum": "sha256:39802c38d96caed2abaa50f38f521209a9d3c0887d26d42acece85016365c56c",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 269
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Vulcan Technologies. Four months. Three founders.",
      "checksum": "sha256:bde3d568880fca3a7bbaafaee65cf01ea1ace4aeaedcaca8477237aea3b9376a",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 276
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "One technical. They beat the consulting firms to a state contract.",
      "checksum": "sha256:98cc42db57757c9a242ec81a332fd27007217ec7a51260b0577df409edcb8a5d",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 282
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "Eleven million dollar seed. The discipline works.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f57aa5b434ddc02d675571ef21ac758fee405110845c6b5ac0f05a5b2a34504f",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 293
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "Skip the CLAUDE dot M D file and every Claude Code session re-derives your decisions from scratch.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b94f5d2968d3381b01a8f6678dbed63c100f3ce9a69bd98121ff94b0782e45b3",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 5.38702947845805,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 300
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "The playbook calls five minutes of docs per session cheap insurance against a codebase that collapses.",
      "checksum": "sha256:92710c63ed568174d3a3de0c099cffa38a46340c3f836255bafa48865fcd2bcd",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 5.758548752834467,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 317
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "So here's the question. Are you running this playbook, or still validating with vibes?",
      "checksum": "sha256:6c244035a97baf1f0c17a73e99483948696f44ec351b8a1696c3d9166264dcb9",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 333
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Drop your stage in the comments. And subscribe for more A I news.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e38c952c07dd8d76e339bb1d1cd84d61c6bd9f43ca473cc432256c66f135e36b",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 347
    }
  ]
}